		{
			dependencies: ["32996B8992B1FF07"]
			description: [
				"Left with no clear answers and the fragments still in your possession, you feel overwhelmed. The path forward is uncertain, but one thing becomes clear: the &6fragments&r hold value when traded with knowledgeable Cartographers, elusive Goblin Traders and maybe someone else? "
				""
				"Perhaps this is the key to unlocking their true power."
				""
				"&o&8\"Though the road has been winding and fraught with dead ends, the fragments are not without worth. Your next step lies in forging alliances and trading wisely.\"&r&r"
			]
